name: Grey 3
description: Grey is a great color for everything. When you think about color, do you think about color compatibility? I’m talking about clothes, weather and your mood and of course, photography. Have you noticed that sometimes black and white photos look a lot more interesting and tastier than colored ones. Of course, if you pick this gray one correctly. So I give a separate place in my heart to this colour for all the misery and joy it has brought me.
